Jacob Kadera and Matilda Kadera, appellants, v. Morava Building & Loan Association, appellee.Gen. No. 25,973.Bill for release of real estate mortgage. Decree for defendant. Appeal from the Superior Court of Cook county; the Hon. Denis E. Sullivan, Judge, presiding. Heard in this court at the March term, 1920.Reversed and remanded with directions.Opinion filed October 11, 1920.

McSurely, J., dissenting.

Certiorari denied by Supreme Court (making opinion final).Otto Kerner, for appellants; James S. Wight, of counsel. George J. Dreiske, for appellee. Mr. Justice Dever

delivered the opinion of the court.
